                    <documentation>
                        <summary>
                            Represents an audit information about the creation of this health 
                            record item.
                        </summary>

                        <remarks>
                            The audit records when the operation happened,
                            by which application, and by which person. The creation audit 
                            information node is returned only by versions of the GetThings method
                            higher than 2.
                        </remarks>
                    </documentation>
